00:40:00,239 --> 00:40:01,800
What kind of weather is this?

597
00:40:03,840 --> 00:40:04,960
It just keeps raining.

598
00:40:07,280 --> 00:40:08,679
Rain is good.

599
00:40:09,280 --> 00:40:10,519
Water brings wealth.

600
00:40:11,679 --> 00:40:12,280
Enough.

601
00:40:13,199 --> 00:40:14,199
Stop cooking dishes and soup.

602
00:40:15,480 --> 00:40:16,440
Did you bring the money?

603
00:40:18,159 --> 00:40:19,159
All you care about is money.

604
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:29,920
That’s not right.

605
00:40:30,719 --> 00:40:31,760
I only brought what I owed last time.

606
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:33,559
The higher-ups are getting suspicious.

607
00:40:34,920 --> 00:40:36,880
They asked why there were two collapses in one month.

608
00:40:38,440 --> 00:40:40,119
Even the King of Hell can’t keep up.

609
00:40:42,360 --> 00:40:43,079
Take it easy.

610
00:40:44,199 --> 00:40:45,559
There have been a lot of collapses.

611
00:40:46,159 --> 00:40:47,719
You take a big cut too.

612
00:40:49,559 --> 00:40:51,239
I do a lot of work myself.

613
00:40:51,840 --> 00:40:52,519
Brother.

614
00:40:53,039 --> 00:40:55,320
I know you’re not easy to fool, Big Safe.

615
00:40:56,320 --> 00:40:57,239
But still,

616
00:40:57,239 --> 00:40:58,679
We agreed on this beforehand.

617
00:41:01,159 --> 00:41:02,519
I’m in charge of bringing in the living.

618
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:03,639
Dragging out the dead.

619
00:41:04,119 --> 00:41:06,119
And pretending to be relatives of the dead for money.

620
00:41:06,719 --> 00:41:08,320
I do just as much as you.

621
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,760
Who told you to bring them into the yard?

622
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:14,000
Bad luck.

623
00:41:14,320 --> 00:41:15,199
Bad luck.

624
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:17,440
Everyone’s seen this kind of thing these days.

625
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:20,159
It’s all pure silver.

626
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:25,760
This wine—

627
00:41:26,199 --> 00:41:27,840
So soft and mellow.

628
00:41:28,159 --> 00:41:29,199
Feels like little hands.

629
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:30,400
It’s deadly tempting.

630
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:32,400
Quit with the nonsense.

631
00:41:33,199 --> 00:41:34,000
Can’t touch, can’t even—

632
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:35,280
Just want to enjoy the taste.

633
00:41:35,440 --> 00:41:36,519
If you don’t shut up,

634
00:41:37,000 --> 00:41:38,119
I’ll cut out your tongue.

635
00:41:38,119 --> 00:41:39,039
And stuff it down your throat.

636
00:41:39,079 --> 00:41:39,599
Fine.

637
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:40,960
I’ll wait for you inside.

638
00:42:24,840 --> 00:42:26,039
Restless spirits, don't haunt me.

639
00:42:27,079 --> 00:42:28,239
Go bother whoever you're looking for.

640
00:42:31,239 --> 00:42:32,119
Let go of me.

641
00:42:32,719 --> 00:42:34,000
I've seen every kind of ghost there is.

642
00:42:34,719 --> 00:42:35,840
Gluttonous ghosts, starving ghosts,

643
00:42:35,840 --> 00:42:37,079
hanged ghosts, drowned ghosts,

644
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:38,559
ghosts who died of illness, ghosts who froze to death,

645
00:42:39,400 --> 00:42:40,760
even drunkards and lechers.

646
00:42:41,280 --> 00:42:42,480
Any ghost who sees me

647
00:42:43,079 --> 00:42:44,159
has to bow their head.

648
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:45,079
and keep their distance.

649
00:42:45,239 --> 00:42:46,480
They all steer clear of me.
